name: CubickRun
description:
CubickRun is a runner-style game created on Unity3D

In this game you will need to pass various levels, collect coins and just have fun. 

There are 5 levels in total in the game

------------------------------------------------------------

Management:

A - Move to the left

D - Move to the right

Space - Jump

G - Camera rotation (Where available)

------------------------------------------------------------
